headline: The Patients Forced to Switch From Zepbound to Wegovy
summary: Some patients reluctantly shifted to save money while others have appealed for coverage of Zepbound after having experienced better weight-loss results and fewer side effects.

headline: Leerink Partners and Jefferies Issue Bullish Ratings on Eli Lilly and Company (LLY)
summary: Eli Lilly and Company (NYSE:LLY) is among the 12 Best Ethical Companies to Invest in 2025. On July 18, Leerink Partners maintained its ‘Buy’ rating on the company, citing growth potential through the GLP-1 receptor agonist (GLP-1RA) […]
